termsconditions.headline: Terms & Conditions
termsconditions.terms: Welcome to the Cheezious Rider App. This Privacy Policy is designed to help you understand how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information. By downloading, installing, or using the App, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.
termsconditions.personal: When you register for and use our App, we may collect personal information, including but not limited to your name, contact details (such as phone number and email address), and profile picture.
termsconditions.location: To facilitate the rider delivery process, we collect and store your location information, including GPS data, when you use our App.
termsconditions.usage: We may collect information about your interactions with the App, such as the orders you make, delivery routes, and device information (e.g., device type, operating system, and version).
termsconditions.payment: If you use our App to make payments, we may collect payment card details. However, we do not store or retain this information. Payment transactions are processed securely through third-party payment processors.
termsconditions.communication: We may collect information related to your communications with us, such as customer support inquiries and feedback.
